y.description: Sets the vertical domain of this map (in plot fraction).

x.description: Sets the horizontal domain of this map (in plot fraction).

lat.description: Rotates the map along meridians (in degrees North).

lon.description: Rotates the map along parallels (in degrees East).

roll.description: Roll the map (in degrees) For example, a roll of *180* makes the map appear upside down.

scale.description: Zooms in or out on the map view.

parallels.description: For conic projection types only. Sets the parallels (tangent, secant) where the cone intersects the sphere.

showframe.description: Sets whether or not a frame is drawn around the map.

showlakes.description: Sets whether or not lakes are drawn.

countrywidth.description: Sets line width (in px) of the country boundaries.

countrycolor.description: Sets line color of the country boundaries.

showsubunits.description: Sets whether or not boundaries of subunits within countries (e.g. states, provinces) are drawn.

bgcolor.description: Set the background color of the map

showcountries.description: Sets whether or not country boundaries are drawn.

riverwidth.description: Sets the stroke width (in px) of the rivers.

scope.description: Set the scope of the map.

subunitcolor.description: Sets the color of the subunits boundaries.

tick0.description: Sets the graticule's starting tick longitude/latitude.

gridwidth.description: Sets the graticule's stroke width (in px).

dtick.description: Sets the graticule's longitude/latitude tick step.

showgrid.description: Sets whether or not graticule are shown on the map.

range.description: Sets the range of this axis (in degrees).

subunitwidth.description: Sets the stroke width (in px) of the subunits boundaries.

showocean.description: Sets whether or not oceans are filled in color.

lakecolor.description: Sets the color of the lakes.

showrivers.description: Sets whether or not rivers are drawn.

showland.description: Sets whether or not land masses are filled in color.

tick0.description: Sets the graticule's starting tick longitude/latitude.

gridwidth.description: Sets the graticule's stroke width (in px).

dtick.description: Sets the graticule's longitude/latitude tick step.

showgrid.description: Sets whether or not graticule are shown on the map.

range.description: Sets the range of this axis (in degrees).

coastlinewidth.description: Sets the coastline stroke width (in px).

showcoastlines.description: Sets whether or not the coastlines are drawn.

framewidth.description: Sets the stroke width (in px) of the frame.

resolution.description: Sets the resolution of the base layers. The values have units of km/mm e.g. 110 corresponds to a scale ratio of 1:110,000,000.
